body:

The 2026 edition of PyCon DE & PyData took place 14–17 April 2026 at the darmstadtium in Darmstadt. Browse the [archived talks](talks/) and [speakers](speakers/) below, or revisit the [original conference site](https://2026.pycon.de/).
